########## Functions for pixelizing spheres  ##############
Datasets
###############
sphere.dat - robjects contianing different pixelized spheres
sphere_centers.dat - dataset contians the coordinates of sphere centers

Functions
################
pixelize -- Pixelizes a space by translating the 
sphere2pix -- creates a sphere centered at 0 with a radius 
arb_pixelize -- Takes in coordindates and radii of spheres and produces a pixelized version of the space




